時，追徵其價額。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TYDM/109%2c%e6%99%ba%e6%98%93%2c24%2c20220208%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TYDM,109,智易,24,20220208,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"智易","JNO":"24","JDATE":"20220208","JTITLE":"詐欺等"}